name: "Boo" by RFY (HF) & FEH (TT)
description: [Felt pen, rub-on images, and foam letters with digital embellishments and color.] My granddaughter, Felicity, and I have created a horrifying, weirdo poster with this piece that explores the clash between meaning and emotional expression. I'm very pleased with this one! ---Richard F. Yates (Holy Fool) & Felicity Echo Hanson (Toddler Terror)
